welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Tembagapura, Indonesia! Known for its stunning natural beauty and warm hospitality, this charming city invites you to immerse yourself in its culture and explore all it has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Timika Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Domestic Terminal
terminals.description: The domestic terminal at Timika Airport handles all domestic flights within Indonesia.

terminals.name: International Terminal
terminals.description: The international terminal at Timika Airport serves flights to and from other countries.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the wifi network for free by selecting the 'Timika Airport Wifi' network and entering the provided password.
